    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The village sits within Southbury and is celebrated for its rural charm and historic character.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.trawellino.com/destinations/united-states/connecticut_heritage-village"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Among its historic structures is the South Britain Congregational Church, a building that dates back to the 18th century.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.trawellino.com/destinations/united-states/connecticut_heritage-village"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Despite its name, Heritage Village is a modern community that hosts more than 20 social clubs, including a yacht club without a body of water.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.trawellino.com/destinations/united-states/connecticut_heritage-village"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "From the nearby train station, visitors can hop on a taxi or bus to reach Heritage Village.",
